<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算不是巨大的化石，<delay8 />
感覺也有很多故事啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是太古的浪漫情懷啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這房間裡的化石
大多是海生動物。<delay20 />
這麼一說，<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />就跟水族館差不多嘛！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我對化石<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也算有點研究。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想，<delay20 />這裡的化石啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是幾億年前的吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">沒想到曾經有<delay8 />
這麼巨大的生物走在這土地上<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這正是古代的浪漫情懷啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這些傢伙全都露出一副不好惹的樣子，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也好想變成這樣啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之這大小最棒啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你應該能懂我吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">化石這東西啊，<delay8 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我原本以為是幾億年前的東西，<delay20 />
但也有年代近一點的喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話雖如此，<delay8 />
但也是幾千萬年前或幾百萬年前啊，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要是我變成化石，會像這樣嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />的頭！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />的身體！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把我挖出來的時候，<delay8 />
盡量挖得完整點喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">每次到這房間來，<delay8 />
都會看到形狀挺眼熟的骨頭啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說是這麼說，<delay20 />但我很少看到<delay8 />
化石以外的骨頭就是了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣？<delay20 />有沒有找到<delay8 />
中意的化石啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />你盡量看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">情侶們<delay8 />不太會來這裡，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就算像我這樣一個人來，<delay8 />
也能放鬆參觀，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的老東西啊，該怎麼說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />令人懷念嗎？<delay20 />有種簡雅的意境啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">化石這東西啊，<delay20 />
可以追溯各種生物的起源，<delay8 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人看著看著，就覺得超興奮的啊！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後我就多來<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />走動走動，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看看有沒有增加新的展覽品，<delay8 />
順便散散步吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />沒想到我們島上
終於也蓋了<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是件值得高興的事咧！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到這間房間<delay8 />
哪天也會堆滿帥氣的化石<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～！<delay20 />就讓我興奮得不得了啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座島上，<delay8 />
終於也開了<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能這麼輕易就看到化石，<delay8 />真令人高興啊。
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說，<delay20 />你注意到地板的圖案了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那一條條的線<delay8 />就像串聯現在跟過去的樹狀圖，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很有型吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>